{"tid":1213623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反送中示威｜行動指揮起底】港島總區高級警司吳樂俊 曾被影猛男寫真 劉公子：佢喺我當年嘅至愛！","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:55:03.000Z","uid":20058,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d30803884885843603f95ae0aa870f4c2e55277d","tid":1213623,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"6月12日各界早已預料會罷工罷市，並會湧去金鐘和立法會一帶示威。警方明言部署警力防備，行動指揮是港島總區高級警司吳樂俊，警隊中人稱他為「警隊黎明」，皆因他高大威猛，貌似黎明。但原來他曾被同志富商劉定成影過猛男寫真。<br />\n2012年吳樂俊捲入「劉公子」劉定成裸照勒索法庭案件。據報導指出，吳樂俊曾被邀協助調查，據稱他曾裸露上衣，只穿短褲讓劉公子影猛男寫真。<br />\n<br />\n話說06年吳樂俊在跑馬地快餐店認識劉公子，劉公子多番游說他擔任模特兒。吳樂俊稱沒收酬勞純粹幫助朋友，於是他前往劉公子跑馬地寓所拍攝，初頭吳樂俊身穿白色背心，其後劉公子要求脫去上衣，稱要營造夏日炎炎的氣氛。他表示事後二人再沒聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n事實上劉公子有一鋪集郵癮，七十年代開始。他影過無數影視男藝人﹑警察肌肉猛男寫真，九五年曾被警方拘捕，警方檢獲十多萬張裸照。劉公子有特殊癖好，會在相片記下姓名、下體尺寸、警員編號等。當時他因證據不足而不被起訴。當年無罪甩身。但他被控非禮及恐嚇一名男模特兒，一二年在區域法院被判罪成，判囚17個月。<br />\n<br />\n壹仔就此事向劉定成查詢，他拋下一句：「吳樂俊喺我當年至愛！」但他以環境嘈雜為由，表示稍後會爆更多內情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_675434_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_675434_0&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=ae928293\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_675434_0&h=b2af7fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_675434_0</a>"},{"pid":"a7da1e5c4785e7c2b249d4a814ba6b69b7f3a492","tid":1213623,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"星期日負責遊行吳樂𢓭警司曾涉劉公子裸照案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8cec766d4a1fca01fbeabaa02fec7f460793f6","tid":1213623,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19cac40b14385ae2543c20d2f84ad98e2cce972","tid":1213623,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd1ed5fc79b6c71c7029b5b7112fb741d96ccff","tid":1213623,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120522/large/22la4p115a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120522%2Flarge%2F22la4p115a.jpg&h=163c0bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src